{"tid":2057441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[BB做咩唔聽我電話] 南韓午後再撥打朝方電話　北韓未有接聽","createTime":"2020-06-09T11:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T11:39:04.000Z","uid":26071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5685f9ba9d6985f6939505f54349727e1192b0","tid":2057441,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:14:47.000Z","msg":"南北韓關係近期轉趨緊張，北韓宣布關閉兩韓之間所有通信聯絡渠道。南韓統一部早上起撥打朝方電話、至中午後再嘗試以通話與北韓聯絡，但朝方都未有接聽。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社形容，韓方工作人員撥打電話時，電話響起接通的聲響，只是對方未有人接聽，未知北韓有否切斷聯絡熱線。統一部促請朝方根據協定維持南北韓之間的基本通信渠道。<br />\n<br />\n今次是兩韓自前年重建聯絡渠道後，北韓首次未有接聽電話。北韓早前因應脫北者在邊境散佈反朝傳單，將對韓工作改為對敵工作，並下令全面關閉兩韓之間所有通信聯絡渠道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531048-20200609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531048-20200609.htm&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=cb3b1df9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531048-20200609.htm&h=fd5dece0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531048-20200609.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n日日都要傾電話<br />\n究竟有咩傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5UJoNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5UJoNJ.jpg&h=461b9cd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a50fd22907d6cc588a2990b0d48ede5b02d8cb84","tid":2057441,"uid":122233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"係咪北韓無刀仔切唔撚斷啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d12bab1d6d1cb80235630efa3dac35a044f8077","tid":2057441,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"之前傾到冇晒分鐘喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191378b38f7d4c8d653fd46018c86341443